  <%- include('partials/layout/header') %>
  <main class="w-full min-h-96">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Get in Touch with Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Thank you for considering Creative Spaces for your landscaping needs. We are committed to providing high-quality services to our clients. Please feel free to contact us with any questions you may have about our services or to schedule a consultation. You can reach us by phone, email, or by using the contact form on this page. We look forward to hearing from you soon.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-2 mt-4">
          <a href="#" class="text-black">
